{"tid":1434832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要破壞古蹟文物","createTime":"2019-08-09T01:35:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:07.000Z","uid":296873,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f8f245eb7ea6c05b0a6a65b95b2da5b8fa260b75","tid":1434832,"uid":296873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:35:22.000Z","msg":"咁多位兄弟姐妹<br />\n我係呢幾次集會都負責後勤<br />\n今次想提提大家<br />\n如果見到有人破壞文物<br />\n懇請大家幫忙阻止<br />\n第一，古蹟文物破壞左就冇，呢個吾應該係我地本意<br />\n第二，吾好因為一時衝動招人話柄，俾人地覺得我地係妄顧下一代歷史<br />\n最後，寄語大家：不割蓆，不篤灰，不指責<br />\n一齊努力加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892df2d9cc8aa269791ef4d27e1e8acdff910ec8","tid":1434832,"uid":249940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:37:44.000Z","msg":"咪濫用不割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fa95012e61bc697be1b0a9062eb715a3964771e","tid":1434832,"uid":138608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"吾你老母"}]}